lead_paragraph: English teenager Jack Harrison stole the show from his famous team mates with a goal and an assist as New York City FC beat New York Red Bulls 2-0 in a Major League Soccer local derby at Yankee Stadium on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Harrison the Hero as New York City Beat Red Bulls at Last
